0 to open the interface
Face recognisation
1)1- System setting
a)volume up- 1 finger Up direction
b)volume down-1 finger Down direction
c)volume mute-2 fingers
d)pause/play-3 fingers
2)2- Mp3 player
a)volume up- 1 finger up direction
b)volume down- 1 finger down direction
c)previous song- 2 finger down direction
d)next song- 2 finger up direction
e)pause/play- 3 fingers
5 to close the interface